READ CAPTION 🚨 New Year’s resolution for my clients: 🥂

•Please start reading all emails! On my scheduling page it says “Read Before Booking” DO THAT! 

• Look for the address before your scheduled appointment to know the amount of time you have to make it to your appointment. Because I am real strict on late fees and cancellations! 

• Know the required payment methods! If my site says no cash app, stop coming to your appointment trying to pay via cash app. 

• Please know your remaining balance before your appointment!

•Please stay off your phone while being serviced. My goal is to have everyone in and out within a timely manner. But if you’re constantly not holding your head up or talking on the phone. It’s impossible 😉 

• Last but not least. RELAX! I love to see my clients relaxing while being serviced! I have a recliner just for that reason! Put those phones down for 45 mins - 1hr and enjoy the service of being glammed!
